commit.message: Commented out potentially bug prone code.
Switched from infrrd.ai API to taggun.io API (for receipt recognition)
Added receipt parsing API connectivity. Encoded image taken to send to external API. Added barebones Retrofit connectivity.
Changed minimum SDK version in build.gradle and added image Base64 encoding for external receipt parsing API.
Add camera feature and Google Natural Language Processing.
